    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017910/extras/9741322c89e6d83dfc9b0a57b0316356.poster.avif?t=1759118255\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017910/extras/9741322c89e6d83dfc9b0a57b0316356.webm?t=1759118255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017910/extras/9741322c89e6d83dfc9b0a57b0316356.mp4?t=1759118255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A top-down, quick-shot arrow game where precision is key. Master explosive, piercing, and homing arrows as you battle relentless foes and navigate unpredictable attacks. Test your skill in the realm of aberrations to save your loyal pet hawk! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017910/extras/fb1def4905b517578443317ddbea8bf5.poster.avif?t=1759118255\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017910/extras/fb1def4905b517578443317ddbea8bf5.webm?t=1759118255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017910/extras/fb1def4905b517578443317ddbea8bf5.mp4?t=1759118255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-4 Episodes to Complete</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast through 90 action-packed levels of running, jumping, and shooting. Each episode features its own unique boss—take them down!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Arrows and Power ups!  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock powerful upgrades and master unique arrows to showcase your skills!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Cosmetics to collect!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Give Alyssa or Blue a fresh, shiny hat every now and then to customize their look.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-100 Achievements to collect!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your skills to the test, collect those achievements, and strive for that coveted S rank!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017910/extras/6e52bf288fed816b41f8782caf9f97a9.poster.avif?t=1759118255\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017910/extras/6e52bf288fed816b41f8782caf9f97a9.webm?t=1759118255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017910/extras/6e52bf288fed816b41f8782caf9f97a9.mp4?t=1759118255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
